    "Sentiment analysis examines individuals' opinions and emotions concerning events, technology, social issues, and experiences (Mamo, 2023).",
    "Sentiment analysis aims to assess the level of positivity or negativity in written content related to a specific subject, such as social media posts, product reviews, news articles, and blogs (Berger et al., 2020; Humphrey & Wang, 2018; Kauffmann et al., 2020).",
